                "invention-title": [
                    "System and method for improving utilization rate of solar energy",
                    "一种提高太阳光能利用率的系统及方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to a system and method for improving the solar energy utilization rate. According to the method, solar energy is converted into circularly polarized light from non-polarized light so as to improve the utilization rate of solar energy, and the method belongs to the technical field of solar energy conversion and utilization. And non-polarized light is converted into circularly polarized light to be matched with a chiral light absorption semiconductor, so that the light energy utilization efficiency is remarkably improved in the aspects of water photolysis hydrogen production, natural photosynthesis, solar cells and the like. The system provided by the invention can realize efficient conversion efficiency from natural light to circularly polarized light, can convert more than 95% of natural light into circularly polarized light, and can adjust the circular polarization direction of light required by an experiment. Catalytic reaction is carried out under the condition of circularly polarized light with chiral matching, so that the hydrogen production rate and the utilization rate of natural light are greatly improved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及一种提高太阳光能利用率的系统及方法。该方法通过将太阳光能由非偏振光转化为圆偏振光以提高光能利用率，属于太阳能转化利用技术领域。将非偏振光转化为圆偏振光以匹配手性吸光半导体，从而在光解水制氢、自然光合作用、太阳能电池等方面显著提升光能利用效率。本发明的系统可以实现高效的由自然光到圆偏振光的转化效率，可以将95％以上的自然光转化为圆偏振光，并且可以调节实验所需要的光的圆偏振方向。在手性匹配的圆偏振光条件下进行催化反应，极大地提高了产氢速率及对自然光的利用率。"
                }
            ]
